      "l2": "Arme",
      "lemma": "Arm",
      "pos": "noun",
      "gender": "m",
      "gloss": "arm",
      "ipa": "aʁm",
      "weave_priority": 4
    },
    {
      "t": "text",
      "l1": ". Each arm can taste, touch, and even make simple choices on its own. Some scientists think the octopus is close to a living alien. It shows us that a mind can be built in a shape completely different from our own."
